et_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https://wa.me/6293089724?text=Tenho%20interesse%20em%20receber%20um%20orcamento\" id=\"facaumorcamento\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">faça um orçamento</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0bded0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d0bded0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9fb0bc e-con-full elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d9fb0bc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d58b9fb e-transform elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d58b9fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_transform_flipX_effect&quot;:&quot;transform&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"667\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1995.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1432\" alt=\"A ideal Soluções Anticorrosivas, especialistas em pintura industrial e revestimentos anticorrosivos de alto desempenho.\" srcset=\"https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1995.webp 667w, https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1995-200x300.webp 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c192a79 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c192a79\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b378694 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b378694\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Principais <font color=\"#0B80DF\">Vantagens.</font></h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d63289 elementor-icon-list--layout-inline elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"1d63289\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items elementor-inline-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Estrutura Resistente</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Rapidez na Montagem</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be8708d elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"be8708d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"242\" data-end=\"333\"><strong>Montagem e Locação de QuickDeck: Plataforma Suspensa Modular com Alta Segurança e Produtividade</strong></p><p data-start=\"398\" data-end=\"739\">A <strong data-start=\"400\" data-end=\"409\">Ideal</strong>, em parceria com empresas líderes em engenharia de acesso, oferece soluções completas para <strong data-start=\"501\" data-end=\"544\">locação e montagem do sistema QuickDeck</strong> — uma <strong data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"592\">plataforma de acesso suspenso modular</strong> de alta performance, ideal para obras complexas, ambientes industriais, refinarias, usinas, plataformas offshore e áreas com restrições de espaço.</p><p data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"1087\">O <strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"756\">QuickDeck</strong> é um <strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"801\">sistema inovador de acesso suspenso</strong> que se destaca por sua <strong data-start=\"825\" data-end=\"867\">estrutura rígida, piso plano e estável</strong>, com <strong data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"913\">rodapés e guarda-corpos normatizados</strong>, permitindo a montagem em <strong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"962\">qualquer geometria</strong>. É a solução ideal para quem busca <strong data-start=\"998\" data-end=\"1035\">segurança, agilidade e eficiência</strong>, superando as limitações dos andaimes tradicionais.</p><h5 data-start=\"1089\" data-end=\"1116\">Vantagens do QuickDeck:</h5><ul data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1620\"><li data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1179\"><p data-start=\"1119\" data-end=\"1179\"><strong data-start=\"1119\" data-end=\"1177\">Montagem em ambientes restritos e geometrias complexas</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1264\"><p data-start=\"1182\" data-end=\"1264\"><strong data-start=\"1182\" data-end=\"1225\">Redução de até 50% no peso da estrutura</strong>, facilitando o transporte e manuseio</p></li><li data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1316\"><p data-start=\"1267\" data-end=\"1316\"><strong data-start=\"1267\" data-end=\"1314\">Diminuição do custo com mão de obra e frete</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1317\" data-end=\"1406\"><p data-start=\"1319\" data-end=\"1406\"><strong data-start=\"1319\" data-end=\"1404\">Plataforma segura para transporte e suporte de ferramentas e equipamentos pesados</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1407\" data-end=\"1462\"><p data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1462\"><strong data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1460\">Aumento significativo da produtividade em campo</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1463\" data-end=\"1542\"><p data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1500\">Sistema até 2 vezes mais seguro</strong> em comparação aos andaimes tradicionais</p></li><li data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1620\"><p data-start=\"1545\" data-end=\"1620\"><strong data-start=\"1545\" data-end=\"1587\">Mais rapidez na montagem e desmontagem</strong>, reduzindo o tempo total da obra</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1622\" data-end=\"1915\">A Ideal conta com <strong data-start=\"1640\" data-end=\"1672\">equipe técnica especializada</strong>, que desenvolve <strong data-start=\"1689\" data-end=\"1740\">projetos personalizados de engenharia de acesso</strong>, com total conformidade às <strong data-start=\"1768\" data-end=\"1816\">normas NR-18, NR-35 e padrões internacionais</strong>. Atendemos diversos setores industriais, oferecendo soluções sob medida para cada tipo de desafio.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-edb3a6c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"edb3a6c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac3eb0a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ac3eb0a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b68af3e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b68af3e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Perguntas Frequentes sobre QuickDeck – Plataforma de Acesso Suspenso</h1>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17d7b61 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"17d7b61\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3eea093 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3eea093\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b87944 elementor-widget elementor-widget-accordion\" data-id=\"2b87944\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"accordion.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-4561\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-4561\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon elementor-accordion-icon-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-closed\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-far-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8zm0 448c-110.5 0-200-89.5-200-200S145.5 56 256 56s200 89.5 200 200-89.5 200-200 200z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">O que é o sistema QuickDeck e para que serve?</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-4561\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-4561\"><p>O <strong data-start=\"2060\" data-end=\"2073\">QuickDeck</strong> é um sistema de <strong data-start=\"2090\" data-end=\"2117\">acesso suspenso modular</strong>, utilizado como plataforma de trabalho segura em locais elevados ou de difícil acesso. Ele oferece <strong data-start=\"2217\" data-end=\"2265\">rigidez, estabilidade e segurança superiores</strong>, sendo ideal para áreas industriais, plataformas offshore, usinas e grandes estruturas metálicas.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-4562\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-4562\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon elementor-accordion-icon-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-closed\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-far-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8zm0 448c-110.5 0-200-89.5-200-200S145.5 56 256 56s200 89.5 200 200-89.5 200-200 200z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">Quais são as principais vantagens do QuickDeck em relação aos andaimes convencionais?</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-4562\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-4562\"><p>Entre os principais benefícios estão: <strong data-start=\"2503\" data-end=\"2522\">redução de peso</strong>, <strong data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2548\">montagem mais rápida</strong>, <strong data-start=\"2550\" data-end=\"2581\">menos mão de obra envolvida</strong>, <strong data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2616\">plataforma estável e contínua</strong>, além de <strong data-start=\"2626\" data-end=\"2652\">melhor custo-benefício</strong> em projetos que exigem acesso em altura com alta complexidade geométrica.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-4563\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-4563\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon elementor-accordion-icon-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-closed\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-far-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8zm0 448c-110.5 0-200-89.5-200-200S145.5 56 256 56s200 89.5 200 200-89.5 200-200 200z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\"> O QuickDeck pode ser montado em qualquer tipo de estrutura?</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-4563\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-4563\"><p>Sim. O sistema permite <strong data-start=\"2825\" data-end=\"2884\">montagem personalizada em diversos formatos geométricos</strong>, inclusive em <strong data-start=\"2899\" data-end=\"2964\">ambientes confinados, estruturas curvas ou com interferências</strong>. Sua modularidade facilita adaptações a diferentes desafios de obra.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-4564\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-4564\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon elementor-accordion-icon-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-closed\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-far-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8zm0 448c-110.5 0-200-89.5-200-200S145.5 56 256 56s200 89.5 200 200-89.5 200-200 200z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-circle\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119 8 8 119 8 256s111 248 248 248 248-111 248-248S393 8 256 8z\"></path></svg></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">A Ideal oferece apenas locação ou também a montagem do QuickDeck?</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-4564\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-4564\"><p>A <strong data-start=\"3117\" data-end=\"3153\">Ideal oferece a solução completa</strong>, incluindo <strong data-start=\"3165\" data-end=\"3262\">locação dos módulos, projeto técnico sob medida e montagem realizada por equipe especializada</strong>, sempre em conformidade com normas de segurança e desempenho exigidas pela legislação.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-80fd74c elementor-align-center elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"80fd74c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https://wa.me/6293089724?text=Tenho%20interesse%20em%20receber%20um%20orcamento\" id=\"facaumorcamento\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">faça um orçamento</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t",
